<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Blog on MeliPlug.info</title><link>https://meliplug.info/tags/blog/</link><description>Recent content in Blog on MeliPlug.info</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 21:01:12 +0900</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://meliplug.info/tags/blog/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>구상 - Rust Blog</title><link>https://meliplug.info/posts/rust-blog/concept/</link><pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 21:01:12 +0900</pubDate><guid>https://meliplug.info/posts/rust-blog/concept/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="rust-배우는-김에-웹개발도-같이-해보자"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#rust-%eb%b0%b0%ec%9a%b0%eb%8a%94-%ea%b9%80%ec%97%90-%ec%9b%b9%ea%b0%9c%eb%b0%9c%eb%8f%84-%ea%b0%99%ec%9d%b4-%ed%95%b4%eb%b3%b4%ec%9e%90"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 Rust 배우는 김에 웹개발도 같이 해보자!
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rust 배우고 있는 와중, 웹개발을 접목하면서 배우려고 블로그를 만들기로 함.&lt;br&gt;
안정화(?) 될때까지는 현재 블로그 테마를 쓸 예정.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="static-site"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#static-site"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 Static Site
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;블로그 사이트이므로, 그냥 html로 빌드하는 사이트를 만들기로 함.&lt;br&gt;
아래 글에서 기본적인 작동 방식을 알았다.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a href="https://kerkour.com/rust-static-site-generator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="external" &gt;https://kerkour.com/rust-static-site-generator&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;사실 개발하고싶은 방향은 fasterthanlime의 블로그이지만, Rust초보인 내가 접근하기 너무 어렵다고 판단했다.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;a href="https://fasterthanli.me/articles/a-new-website-for-2020" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="external" &gt;https://fasterthanli.me/articles/a-new-website-for-2020&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="cms"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#cms"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 CMS?
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;일반적인 개발 블로그처럼 Markdown을 이용하기로 했다.&lt;br&gt;
Markdown을 parse하는데 이용할 툴은, &lt;a href="https://github.com/wooorm/markdown-rs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="external" &gt;markdown-rs&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Twemoji 쓰기</title><link>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-10-12-twemoji/</link><pubDate>Tue, 12 Oct 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-10-12-twemoji/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="만들기"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%a7%8c%eb%93%a4%ea%b8%b0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 만들기
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class='var'&gt;📝_includes\footer\custom.html&lt;/span&gt;에 다음 코드를 추가해 주면 끝!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;{% include code title=&amp;lsquo;custom.html&amp;rsquo; %}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-html" data-lang="html"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;script&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;src&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;https://twemoji.maxcdn.com/2/twemoji.min.js&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="nx"&gt;twemoji&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;parse&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;document&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;body&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nx"&gt;ext&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;.svg&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nx"&gt;folder&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;svg&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;});&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;lt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;script&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;❗이제는 이모지를 콜론 &lt;code&gt;:&lt;/code&gt; 으로 감싸면 안됩니다!
그냥 이모지 패널을 &lt;code&gt;Win&lt;/code&gt;{: .key .sp}+&lt;code&gt;;&lt;/code&gt;{: .key.h}로 열어서 써주세요!
{: .notice&amp;ndash;success}&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>블로그에 쓸모있는 기능들 추가하기</title><link>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-10-10-utility/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Oct 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-10-10-utility/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="만들것"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%a7%8c%eb%93%a4%ea%b2%83"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 만들것
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#%e2%80%8e%eb%af%b8%eb%a6%ac%eb%b3%b4%ea%b8%b0" class="internal" &gt;따옴표 모양 인용문&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#%eb%af%b8%eb%a6%ac%eb%b3%b4%ea%b8%b0" class="internal" &gt;코드 파일 제목&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="인용문"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%9d%b8%ec%9a%a9%eb%ac%b8"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 인용문
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="미리보기"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%af%b8%eb%a6%ac%eb%b3%b4%ea%b8%b0"&gt;##&lt;/a&gt;
 ‎미리보기
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0"&gt;&lt;code class="language-liquid" data-lang="liquid"&gt;{% raw %}{% include quote text=&amp;#34;바나난 마시따!&amp;#34; by=&amp;#34;고앵이&amp;#34; %}{% endraw %}


{% raw %}{% include quote text=&amp;#34;천재는 99% 의 노력과 &amp;lt;br&amp;gt;1% 의 영감으로 이루어진다&amp;#34; by=&amp;#34;에디슨&amp;#34; %}{% endraw %}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;{% include quote text=&amp;ldquo;바나난 마시따!&amp;rdquo; by=&amp;ldquo;고앵이&amp;rdquo; %}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;{% include quote text=&amp;ldquo;천재는 99% 의 노력과 &lt;br&gt;1% 의 영감으로 이루어진다&amp;rdquo; by=&amp;ldquo;에디슨&amp;rdquo; %}&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이런 느낌?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="만들기"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%a7%8c%eb%93%a4%ea%b8%b0"&gt;##&lt;/a&gt;
 ‎만들기
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📂includes 폴더에 📝quote 라는 파일을 만듭니다.(확장자가 없습니다!!)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>키보드 모양</title><link>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-09-10-keys/</link><pubDate>Fri, 10 Sep 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-09-10-keys/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;그냥 블로그 꾸미다가 필요해서 추가하게 됐다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="소개"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%86%8c%ea%b0%9c"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
 소개
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;A&lt;/code&gt;{: .key} ⬅대충 이런 거. &lt;strong&gt;누를 수도 있다!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="만들기"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%a7%8c%eb%93%a4%ea%b8%b0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 만들기
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;먼저 📁&lt;code&gt;_sass\mininmal-mistakes&lt;/code&gt; 폴더에 📝&lt;code&gt;_keys.scss&lt;/code&gt; 파일을 만듭니다.
다음 내용을 작성합니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="_keysscss"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#_keysscss"&gt;##&lt;/a&gt;
 📄_keys.scss
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-css" data-lang="css"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;//&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;Keys&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nc"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;color&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mh"&gt;#000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;font-family&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kc"&gt;monospace&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;font-weight&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kc"&gt;bold&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;background&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mh"&gt;#fff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;align-items&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kc"&gt;center&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;display&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kc"&gt;inline-block&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;border&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;margin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;padding&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;padding-right&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;padding-left&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;box-shadow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mh"&gt;#fff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mh"&gt;#bbb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;cursor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="kc"&gt;pointer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;transition&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;s&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;cubic-bezier&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nc"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nd"&gt;active&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;top&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;	&lt;span class="k"&gt;box-shadow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mh"&gt;#fff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mf"&gt;.05&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;em&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mh"&gt;#bbb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="minimal-mistakesscss-에-임포트-하기"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#minimal-mistakesscss-%ec%97%90-%ec%9e%84%ed%8f%ac%ed%8a%b8-%ed%95%98%ea%b8%b0"&gt;##&lt;/a&gt;
 📄minimal-mistakes.scss 에 임포트 하기
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;그후 📁&lt;code&gt;_sass&lt;/code&gt; 폴더에 📄&lt;code&gt;minimal-mistakes.scss&lt;/code&gt; 파일을 열고 마지막줄에 다음 내용을 입력합니다.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>깃헙 블로그 시작</title><link>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-08-21-blogstart/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 Aug 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://meliplug.info/posts/old/blog/2021-08-21-blogstart/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="블로그-소개"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%b8%94%eb%a1%9c%ea%b7%b8-%ec%86%8c%ea%b0%9c"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 블로그 소개
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;일단 주요 포스팅은 &lt;strong&gt;마인크래프트 리소스팩&lt;/strong&gt; 입니다.
그 외에도 파이썬, HTML 등 코딩도 할 예정&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;블로그를 하는 이유는&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;내가 배운거 메모(?)하는 목적&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;다른사람이 보고 배워가면 해서&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;말투(?) 가 왔다 갔다 할 수 있습니다.(존댓말, 반말 등)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;완전히 &lt;em&gt;생&lt;/em&gt;초보를 위한 블로그인 동시에 필자 또한 생초보이기 때문에 매우 매우 쉽게 설명하고 있습니다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="코드에-관하여"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ec%bd%94%eb%93%9c%ec%97%90-%ea%b4%80%ed%95%98%ec%97%ac"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 코드에 관하여
